*** 0.4.4-maki ***
- add enum string mapping to model layout.
- fix little bug in "non session stored" forms.
- fix PHP crash (on wampserver) when adding js scripts in Page constructor.
- add some jQuery support.
- add jQuery UI Tabs Layout.

*** 0.4.3-maki ***
- Rename *Record_Table* classes to *Grid* classes
- Add number input layout
- Fix Ea_Xml_Element encoding issue (SimpleXmlElement cannot be easily extended ;p) and implement encoding interface

*** 0.4.2-maki ***
- Fix minor bugs for not session stored forms
- Fix minor bugs in date input
- Fix minor bugs with "cross module" form use
- Security : allow use of getUserXXX() methods when no user connected and rename getConnectedUserXXX() methods in getUserXXX()
- Add flash layout
- Add label for inputs and modify checkout and radio constructor
- Refresh the attributes code for layouts
- Add Google Map v3 Layout
- Add Google Map Geocoder service
- Add "label for" to checkbox and radio input
- Introduce encoding interface

*** 0.4.1-maki ***
Consolidation release.
- Message Layout / setMessage()
- ereg functions deprecated => preg functions
- Fix minor issue with containers
- Fix bugs on date format in data/layout models
- Add Date Input Layout
- Modify form model layout to use date input

*** 0.4.0-maki ***
Improve form support :
- modules can "auto manage" forms : submit callbacks added to forms can be auto triggered.
Improve layout support :
- can add() array of layouts
Improve records table :
- rethink of populate() method to allow raw record (ie : non data records) 
Simplify url params :
- can use application range params (no more module prefix in urls => same as raw param)

*** 0.3.8-snow ***
Improve form support :
- add submit callback
Improve Session Namespace support :
- add namespace/appname for session
Change Ea_Router in Ea_App ;p
- Ea_Router is still present for compatibility

*** 0.3.7-snow ***
Minor bug fixes :
- correct bug in links.

*** 0.3.6-snow ***
Improve model layout :
- layout model metadata "heritage" from data model.
- you can create layout model without data model.

*** 0.3.5-snow ***
Improve form support :
- redesign of file upload methods.
- add better support for input's name in record table.
- fix session bugs on Ea_Layout_Form::store()
Improve router :
- add app name for session namespaces.
- all sessions are in app namespace.

*** 0.3.4-snow ***
Change version numbering.
Improve security layer :
- add anonymous role.
Improve layer model :
- add postRender() method.
Improve record table :
- add row modifier.

*** 0.0.3.3-dumb ***
Basic batch support.
Multiple select support.
Improve security layer :
- add public role.
- fix minor bug.

*** 0.0.3.2-dumb ***
Improve Zend_Db pdo support in model :
- select statement model support
- support for PDO_OCI data in model
- partial support for Oracle CLOB
Add XML model support :
- model can be load from xml files.

*** 0.0.3.1-dumb ***
Improve form support :
- GET form can be use to build route (search criteria, etc)
Improve layout model :
- header adapter to generate complex headers (ie. sort headers)
Fix bugs on form.

*** 0.0.3.0-dumb ***
Introduce data model in EasyPhpApp :
